# Where Does Everything Run?

| Component   | Runs On           |
| ----------- | ----------------- |
| Mobile App  | User's phone      |
| Backend     | Cloud server      |
| Database    | Cloud database    |
| PDF Storage | Cloud storage     |
| OCR         | Cloud OCR service |
| AI          | AI API            |

Everything communicates securely over HTTPS.

