# Releasing a New Version

Suppose you fix a bug.

Workflow:

```text
Fix Code

↓

Test

↓

Deploy Backend

↓

Publish Mobile Update

↓

Users Receive New Version
```

Backend fixes can often be deployed without waiting for users to update the app.

